WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Anna goes to a primary school.

00:03.000 --> 00:05.000
She will finish school 
 next year after the 8th grade.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
Anna has to walk three kilometres to school.

00:10.000 --> 00:11.000
She does not own a bicycle,

00:12.000 --> 00:13.000
because bicycles are expensive.

00:14.000 --> 00:17.000
After school, 
 Anna helps her mother in the household,

00:18.000 --> 00:21.000
takes care of the chickens and tends the small garden.
